data.description: This beautiful South Shore greystone 2-flat is a must-see! Just minutes away from the Obama Presidential Library that is currently being built. This 2-unit building is full of beautiful upgrades, including white quartz countertops, elegant blue glass tile backsplash, gray 36 in. shaker cabinets, ceramic tile floor, five-burner 36 in. oven with convection option, & 36 in. overhead hood. Stainless steel appliances include dishwasher, refrigerator, & stove. Bathrooms have modern faucets, shower head combo, vanity sinks, & full-size bathtub. Each unit has 1,300 sq ft of living space. The 1st floor unit, which has the capability of being duplexed-down to the basement that is waiting to be finished, has 2 bedrooms & 1.1 bathrooms. The 2nd floor has 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, which includes a master bedroom & master bath.
